\begin_layout Standard
下面的nonlocal拉氏量是
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

味夸克和
\begin_inset Formula $N^{2}-1$
\end_inset

个Goldstone (GB)玻色子：nonlocal chiral quark model
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathcal{L}_{\text{NCQM}}(x,y)=\bar{\psi}\left(x\right)\delta\left(x-y\right)\gamma.\partial\psi\left(y\right)+\bar{\psi}\left(x\right)\Sigma_{\pi}\left(x,y\right)\psi\left(y\right)
\]

\end_inset

其中，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Sigma_{\pi}\left(x,y\right)=1-\frac{i}{F_{0}}\gamma^{5}\left[\pi\left(x\right)+\pi\left(y\right)\right]-\frac{1}{2F_{0}^{2}}\left[\pi\left(x\right)^{2}+\pi\left(x\right)\pi\left(y\right)+\pi\left(y\right)\pi\left(x\right)+\mathcal{O}\left(\pi^{3}\right)\right]
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\Sigma_{\pi}\left(x,y\right)$
\end_inset

只是
\begin_inset Formula $\left(x-y\right)$
\end_inset

的函数。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
GB 场包含在矩阵中
\begin_inset Formula $\pi\left(z\right)\equiv\lambda^{a}\pi_{a}\left(z\right)$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda^{a}$
\end_inset

是 SU(N) 群的生成元，
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $\tr\left(\lambda^{a},\lambda^{b}\right)=\frac{1}{2}\delta_{ab}$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula $F_{0}$
\end_inset

取决于
\begin_inset Formula $\pi$
\end_inset

场的适当归一化。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
拉氏量中包含一个动力学quark质量
\begin_inset Formula $\Sigma\left(x-y\right)$
\end_inset

，在一个渐进自由的规范理论中应该存在。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
动力学质量是规范理论中，手征对称性自发破缺的序参数，相应的Goldstone玻色子作为非定域序参数的涨落。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
忽略
\begin_inset Formula $F^{\mu\nu}F_{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset

项的规范相互作用为，
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
S_{g} & =\int\dif^{4}x\,\bar{\psi}\left(x\right)\gamma^{\mu}\left(\partial_{\mu}-ieQ\mathcal{A}_{\mu}\right)\psi\left(x\right)\\
 & +\iint\dif^{4}x\dif^{4}y\,\bar{\psi}\left(x\right)\,\Sigma\left(x-y\right)\exp\left(-ieQ\int_{x}^{y}\mathcal{A}_{\nu}\dif\omega^{\nu}\right)\psi\left(y\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

对振幅的local贡献为（L for local，NL for NonLocal）
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
ie\Gamma_{\text{L}}^{\mu}\left(x,y,z\right)=-\frac{\delta^{3}S_{\text{L}}}{\delta\mathcal{A}_{\mu}(x)\,\delta\psi(y)\,\delta\bar{\psi}(z)}\rvert_{\mathcal{A}_{\mu}=0}
\]

\end_inset

这个泛函偏导总是先对 
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\psi}$
\end_inset

 求，再对 
\begin_inset Formula $\psi$
\end_inset

 求。用
\begin_inset Formula $\exp\left[i\left(p^{\prime}\cdot z-p\cdot y-q\cdot x\right)\right]$
\end_inset

进行傅立叶变换，拿掉通常的
\begin_inset Formula $\left(2\pi\right)^{4}\delta\left(p^{\prime}-p-q\right)$
\end_inset

，得到：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
ie\Gamma_{\text{L}}^{\mu}\left(p,q,p+q\right)=ieQ\gamma^{\mu}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
非定域部分困难一些。首先，为了方便，对
\begin_inset Formula $S_{\text{NL}}$
\end_inset

进行导数展开，令：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
F(x,y)=\exp\left(-ieQ\int_{x}^{y}\mathcal{A}^{\nu}\left(\omega\right)\dif\omega_{\nu}\right)\,\psi\left(y\right)
\]

\end_inset

进行傅立叶变换，把
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
S_{\text{NL}} & =\iint\dif^{4}x\dif^{4}y\,\bar{\psi}\left(x\right)\,\Sigma\left(x-y\right)\,\exp\left[-ieQ\int_{x}^{y}\dif\omega^{\nu}\mathcal{A}_{\nu}\left(\omega\right)\right]\psi\left(y\right)\\
 & =\iint\dif^{4}x\dif^{4}y\,\bar{\psi}\left(x\right)\,\Sigma\left(x-y\right)\,F\left(x,y\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

通过
\begin_inset Formula $\exp\left[i\left(p^{\prime}z-py-qx\right)\right]$
\end_inset

变成
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
S_{\text{NL}}=\frac{1}{(2\pi)^{8}}\iint\dif^{4}x\dif^{4}y\,\bar{\psi}\left(k\right)\tilde{\Sigma}\left(p\right)F\left(k-p,p\right)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
部分傅里叶变换
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
假设作用量中的各个场或函数均存在傅立叶变换，写出作用量在动量空间的形式：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\iint\dif^{4}x\dif^{4}y\,\bar{\psi}\left(x\right)\Sigma\left(x-y\right)F\left(x,y\right) & =\frac{1}{\left(2\pi\right)^{4}}\dif^{4}k\,\bar{\psi}\left(k\right)\,\exp\left({\color{red}+}ik.x\right)\\
 & \times\frac{1}{\left(2\pi\right)^{4}}\dif^{4}p\,\tilde{\Sigma}\left(p\right)\,\exp\left[{\color{red}-}ip\left(x-y\right)\right]\\
 & \times\frac{1}{\left(2\pi\right)^{8}}\dif^{4}k_{3}\dif^{4}k_{4}\,F\left(k_{3},k_{4}\right)\,\exp\left[{\color{red}-}ik_{3}.x{\color{red}-}ik_{4}.y\right]
\end{align*}

\end_inset

这里傅立叶变换的符号正负，与后面一一对应。先对
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

积分，平面波因子变成 
\begin_inset Formula $\delta$
\end_inset

 函数：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{\left(2\pi\right)^{4}}\int\dif^{4}x\,\exp\left(ik.x-ip.x-ik_{3}.x\right)\to\delta\left(k-p-k_{3}\right)
\]

\end_inset

再对
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

积分，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{\left(2\pi\right)^{4}}\int\dif^{4}y\,\exp\left(ip.y-ik_{4}.y\right)\to\delta\left(p-k_{4}\right)
\]

\end_inset

最后，使用
\begin_inset Formula $\delta$
\end_inset

函数对
\begin_inset Formula $k_{3},k_{4}$
\end_inset

积分，
\begin_inset Formula $\delta$
\end_inset

 函数将保证动量守恒，限制自由动量的数目，我们得到
