\begin_layout Standard
总结规范变换的约定：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & B\left(x\right)=e^{+ie_{B}^{q}\theta\left(x\right)}B^{\prime}\left(x\right),\quad B^{\prime}\left(x\right)=e^{-ie_{B}^{q}\theta\left(x\right)}B\left(x\right)=U_{B}\left(x\right)B\left(x\right),\\
